(118, 'Notes:: I met him yesterday and Maybe + for DeVC for a 100-200k cheque including angels for me. Spikey 0.5-1 with a clear spike on strategic thinking / execution that comes across through how he has built out / pivoted his last business (healthy company even though not large outcome) and his journey to get to strong flywheels with this one + SourceX is the hidden flywheel here – he’s created a B2B tool for all shoe resellers to list their products across his + other shoe marketplaces making the reseller life a lot easier (reseller-specific unicommerce) + As a result, he has 16000 unique catalogue, while next largest marketplace has 800 + This drives strong word of mouth in a segment where demand isn’t an issue, and shows up in high marketing ROI – 11-12L spend for a 3cr+ GMV (and net of 45L for him) + His growth will come from building this across hype resale categories (is launching for watches and t shirts) + Taking the same platform global – India is a small part of the global reseller market His round with Infoedge is closed (2mn at 10.5 post he said). I’m pushing him to speak to Collective members and see if we can top up in this round if there is excitement at our side. From him, he sees value of getting angels who can help him - Go across categories and build out the marketplace model - Go international at the right time
